        <content>
          <p>CHAPTER 2.  DIVORCE UNDER CIVIL CODE ARTICLE 102
Art. 3951.  Petition for divorce
A petition for divorce under Civil Code Article 102 shall contain allegations of jurisdiction and venue and shall be verified by the affidavit of the petitioner.</p>
        </content>
